name: Station 13010 - Soul
description:
Null Node is a moment of junction. A point of endless potential. Angel's song that you hear a second before the oblivion: ‘...the wind rushing round my open heart, an open ravine... in my spirit white, totally alive, totally relieved.’
Bells ring. Null.
